  {# ── Do's / Don't ── #}
  <h2 id="dos-dont"  class="vf-u-margin--0 vf-u-padding__top--400 vf-u-padding__bottom--600 vf-search-client-side--no-index">Do / Don't</h2>

  <h4>Do</h4>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Serve HTML first</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Defer non-critical JS</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Lazy-load interactivity</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Test under 2G and CPU throttling</li>
  </ul>

  <h4>Don't</h4>
  <ul class="vf-list vf-list--unordered">
    <li class="vf-list__item">Block content behind JavaScript</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Ship large hydration bundles by default</li>
    <li class="vf-list__item">Use SPA-only architecture for content pages</li>
  </ul>


